cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.MA, cs.DC 

The paper deals with the control of large queueing networks, which is a problem in systems engineering and control theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems). The use of simulations and network models suggests that it could also belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) or cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
